ent-ShipVoucherScorpion = PDV Scorpion/Scarab LPC [T1]
    .desc = A small card that authorizes the procurement of either a Scorpion- or Scarab-class escort from the flagship's reserves.

ent-ShipVoucherLuxury = ADF Luxury LPC
    .desc = A small card that authorizes the procurement of a Luxury-class imperial yacht from the Citadel shipyard reserves. Reusable with an eight-hour cooldown between purchases.

ent-ComputerShipyardCitadel = Citadel shipyard console
    .desc = Used to commission imperial yachts from the Citadel shipyard reserves. Requires a valid Citadel LPC.
